result.title: 2011 - 2011 Centre for Environment, Fisheries & Aquaculture Science (Cefas) English Channel and Celtic Sea - Sardine and Anchovy Plankton Survey
result.name: 2011-2011-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-english-channel-and-celtic
result.notes:
Numbers of fish eggs and larvae from plankton samples collected on two pelagic 
surveys (RV Platessa 10/2010 and RV Endeavour 09/2011) to assess population 
structure of sardine and other small pelagic fish species (anchovy, herring, 
sprat, horse mackerel, mackerel, boarfish, blue whiting). Dataset includes 
associated positional data and sample volumes filtered of the plankton 
stations.
